OL,4,G0140FCanals: The Making of a Nation
OL,5,     GLiz McIvor recounts the story of
OL,6,     G'canal mania', the period of
OL,7,     Gactivity that helped develop
OL,8,     GBritain's modern financial
OL,9,     Geconomy, now centred in London.
OL,10,G0210FCanal Walks with Julia Bradbury
OL,11,     GJulia Bradbury walks alongside
OL,12,     Gthe Caledonian Canal in the
OL,13,     GScottish Highlands and tells the
OL,14,     Gstory of Thomas Telford, who
OL,15,     Gcreated this engineering marvel.
OL,16,G0240FThe Normans
OL,17,     GDocumentary series. A look at how
OL,18,     Gthe Normans developed from a band
OL,19,     Gof marauding Vikings into the
OL,20,     Gformidable warriors who conquered
OL,21,     GEngland in 1066.
